metadata.title: PICES Scientific Report No. 9 (1998) - PICES Climate Change and Carrying Capacity Workshop on the Development of Cooperative Research in Coastal Regions of the North Pacific : October 17-18, Pusan, Republic of Korea / Sponsored by PICES-GLOBEC, CC...
metadata.description:
This scientific report identifies the PICES member nations national research programs and the areas for cooperative search experiments in support of the CCCC Program.
